{"tid":989203,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[最新成交] 嘉湖兩房425萬售、沙田第一城426萬售","createTime":"2019-01-20T16:06:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-21T07:27:15.000Z","uid":62935,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"fa00609080bb17063b133cfbf9a80f10a0f7e9c2","tid":989203,"uid":62935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T16:06:03.000Z","msg":"嘉湖山莊低層戶減價出售　呎價9487元<br />\n<br />\n祥益謝利官表示，天水圍嘉湖山莊賞湖居3座低層E室，實用面積448方呎，兩房間隔，去年中叫價550萬元，期後因市況不斷減價。<br />\n<br />\n他亦稱，本月初上址已減至430萬元，低於市價，加上租客終於願意開門睇樓，日前於一小時內吸引7組睇樓客參觀，議價後終連租約售425萬元，呎價9,487元。<br />\n<br />\n原業主2009年10月以125萬元購入，持貨9年帳面獲利300萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連租約...唔計啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另一單沙一 426萬...緊跟嘉湖步伐...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知係咪連租約低層事故單位漏水滲水近垃圾房頂樓無lift對正墳場啦...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6877b51ca228cc4bfdd2803bdc4676ed3351bd36","tid":989203,"uid":28245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T16:09:36.000Z","msg":"450 萬諗邊度好？"},{"pid":"59be704929456bc564534a10a53eee90f07fb68d","tid":989203,"uid":17765,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T16:10:11.000Z","msg":"唔關保升事 唔計"},{"pid":"e1d7c4903f79c7ccc8abeffa36659c48919e1e5d","tid":989203,"uid":10101,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T16:12:03.000Z","msg":"早兩日嘉湖兩房先490成交<br />\n今次唔計啦"},{"pid":"e4bf3f9ece946be4f47461f503b98c7fd1346b18","tid":989203,"uid":8717,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T16:14:08.000Z","msg":"連租約一向要平1成，不過都算平。"},{"pid":"99392e04d9455fec90ccf9ee0df5b214fb8d2269","tid":989203,"uid":62935,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e4bf3f9ece946be4f47461f503b98c7fd1346b18","tid":989203,"uid":8717,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T16:14:08.000Z","msg":"連租約一向要平1成，不過都算平。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-20T16:16:23.000Z","msg":"低層平多半成<br />\n圍番...即係四百尾<br /